}}'''土耳其共和国中央银行'''（{{Lang-tr|Türkiye Cumhuriyet Merkez Bankası, TCMB}}）是[[土耳其|土耳其]]的[[中央银行|中央银行]]。其职责包括执行货币和汇率政策，管理土耳其的[[外汇储备|外匯储备]]，印制和发行纸币，建立、维护和管理土耳其国内的支付系统。土耳其法律规定，土耳其央行的任务是维持土耳其的价格和金融稳定，并有权自行决定任何政策工具<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20190917005908/https://tcmb.gov.tr/wps/wcm/connect/EN/TCMB+EN/Main+Menu/About+The+Bank/At+a+Glance "Duties and Responsibilities"], CBRT. </ref><ref name="CBRT Factsheet">[http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/iletisimgm/Factsheet.php Central Bank of the Republic of Turkey Factsheet] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131125014516/http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/iletisimgm/Factsheet.php#|date=2013-11-25}}, CBRT Official Website, 2012.</ref>。

